snippet.title: Thoughts on Thinking
snippet.description:
Thoughts on Thinking is a channel focusing on psychology and philosophy to search for and reveal higher levels of depth surrounding complex ideas about the human psyche and our expression upon the world.

SUPPORT ME ON PATREON (thank you!) https://www.patreon.com/thoughtsonthinking
